ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities

类 Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.SourceCodeChange
      • ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.Move

  • public class Move
extends SourceCodeChange
    Source code change that represents the move of an entity.

    In addition to the involved entities described in SourceCodeChange an insert has a

    • SourceCodeEntity oldParentEntity that describes from which entity changedEntity is deleted. Speaking of an AST, parentEntity describes the node in which changedEntity was a child before move. parentEntity is taken from the left AST, i.e., old version.
    • SourceCodeEntity newParentEntity that describes in which entity changedEntity is inserted. Speaking of an AST, parentEntity describes the node in which changedEntity will be a child after the move. parentEntity is taken from the left AST, i.e., old version. In case parentEntity was inserted (see SourceCodeChange), it is taken from the right AST.
    • SourceCodeEntity newEntity that describes which entity changedEntity becomes after the move. newEntity is taken from the right AST, i.e., new version.
    作者:
    Beat Fluri, zubi
    另请参阅:

        Creates a new move operation.

        The moved entity is moved from the old to the new parent entity inside the structure entity.

        参数:
        changeType - the change type
        rootNode - the root node
        movedEntity - the moved entity
        newEntity - the new entity
        oldParentEntity - the old parent entity
        newParentEntity - the new parent entity
